ss%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20CEOs'%20enthusiasm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agentic-ai-agents-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20always%20up%20to%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20culprit%3A%20hallucinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20are%20software%20programs%20that%20can%20perform%20tasks%20independently%2C%20such%20as%20reconciling%20an%20invoice%2C%20so%20that%20a%20person%20doesn't%20have%20to.%20Sounds%20great%2C%20right%3F%20That's%20why%20companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagentic-internet-ai-rails-google-anthropic-openai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplugging%20agents%20into%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20sales%2C%20finance%2C%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20while%20agentic%20systems%20can%20be%20effective%20at%20completing%20discrete%20tasks%2C%20they%20can%20be%20fragile%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErrors%20can%20quickly%20become%20a%20bottleneck%20if%20hallucinations%20multiply%20when%20agents%20interact%2C%20said%20Nicolas%20Darveau-Garneau%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20executive%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Ded665f43646842b043ded56bff9bb1a45b4b454767cbd99a0b4443fe12a6efa7%26postID%3D698a4fedb2b73923d9cd025b%26postSlug%3Dai-agents-taking-on-work-challenge-of-scaling-2026-2%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSequoia-Not-Bonsai-Successful-Companies%252Fdp%252F1400254248%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBe%20a%20Sequoia%2C%20Not%20a%20Bonsai%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20single%20agent%20has%20a%205%25%20hallucination%20rate%2C%20then%20it's%20hard%20to%20daisy-chain%20multiple%20agents%20without%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20errors.%20That's%20because%20the%20risk%20increases%20exponentially%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Ins