Amazon%20rolled%20out%20internal%20guidance%20steering%20teams%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-kiro-project-ai-agents-software-coding-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKiro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20in-house%20AI%20coding%20assistant%2C%20according%20to%20internal%20messages%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20guidance%20encourages%20using%20Kiro%20over%20non-approved%20third-party%20tools%2C%20including%20Claude%20Code%2C%20for%20production%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20prompted%20criticism%20across%20internal%20Amazon%20forums.%20In%20one%20discussion%20thread%2C%20roughly%201%2C500%20Amazon%20employees%20endorsed%20the%20formal%20adoption%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20according%20to%20the%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20have%20been%20particularly%20awkward%20for%20engineers%20who%20help%20sell%20AWS%20Bedrock%2C%20Amazon's%20platform%20that%20offers%20customers%20access%20to%20third-party%20AI%20services%2C%20including%20Claude%20Code.%20Some%20questioned%20how%20they%20could%20credibly%20promote%20a%20product%20they%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20use%20themselves%20in%20official%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20will%20ask%20why%20they%20should%20trust%20or%20use%20a%20tool%20that%20we%20did%20not%20approve%20for%20internal%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20highlights%20the%20complexity%20of%20Amazon's%20relationship%20with%20Anthropic.%20While%20Amazon%20is%20racing%20to%20build%20and%20promote%20its%20own%20AI%20tools%2C%20it%20is%20also%20marketing%20a%20partner's%20competing%20technology.%20Amazon%20is%20one%20of%20Anthropic's%20largest%20investors%2C%20with%20a%20stake%20valued%20at%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-bet-anthropic-soars-61-billion-valuation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2460%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Anthropic%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20a%20major%20AWS%20customer%2C%20committing%20to%20use%20Amazon's%20cloud%20services%20and%20at%20least%20one%20million%20of%20Amazon's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cloud-matt-garman-ai-bets-layoffs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainium%3C%2Fa%3E%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20incredible%20improvements%20in%20efficiency%20and%20delivery%20from%20Kiro%2C%20our%20customer%20growth%20is%20rapidly%20accelerating%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20internal%20employees%20all%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%20capability%20to%20deliver%20faster%20for%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20continue%20to%20support%20existing%20tools%20in%20use%20today%2C%20we%20do%20not%20plan%20to%20support%20additional%2C%20third-party%20AI%20development%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20maintains%20%26quot%3Ba%20strong%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20Anthropic%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20while%20there's%20no%20explicit%20ban%20on%20Claude%20Code%2C%20the%20company%20applies%20%26quot%3Bstricter%20requirements%20for%20the%20tools%20used%20to%20develop%20production%20code%20specifically%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20Amazon%20provides%20a%20process%20for%20seeking%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Anthropic%20spokesperson%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a269ce34-c2ac-4b8c-a980-b521a5eabe6b%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSurvival%20mechanism%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20internal%20forums%2C%20an%20Amazon%20sales%20engineer%20flagged%20the%20irony%20of%20being%20asked%20to%20sell%20Claude%20Code%20even%20though%20it%20isn't%20formally%20supported%20inside%20the%20company.%20The%20employee%20wrote%20that%20they%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%2C%20demo%2C%20and%20build%26quot%3B%20with%20Claude%20Code%20to%20support%20Amazon's%20directive%20to%20get%2