quot%3B%20This%20is%20what%20I%20choose%20for%20my%20lunch%20finale%2C%20adding%20a%20quarter%20of%20an%20avocado%20as%20my%20%26quot%3Bother%20thing.%26quot%3B%20It's%20pretty%20good%2C%20though%20I%20have%20to%20embiggen%20it%20from%20the%20description%20to%20make%20it%20actually%20filling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreakfast%3A%201%20corn%20tortilla%20with%202%20slices%20of%20cheddar%20cheese%2C%20%C2%BC%20avocado%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELunch%3A%20The%20Brooke%20Rollins%20Special%20%E2%80%94%201%20corn%20tortilla%2C%20chicken%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20%C2%BC%20avocado%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinner%3A%20Ground%20beef%20and%20chickpea%20skillet%20with%20broccoli%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%3A%20Victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20tortilla%20with%20broccoli%20and%20chicken%20and%20avocado%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698a352be1ba468a96abb38d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThank%20you%2C%20Secretary%20Rollins%2C%20for%20the%20inspiration.%20Honestly%2C%20it%20was%20pretty%20good.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Stewart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e1da776-26cc-4ad7-bc37-5e5032a79864%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20did%20I%20learn%20from%20the%20diet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20the%20RFK%20diet%20on%20a%20%24105-a-week%20food%20plan%20was%20not%20as%20hard%20as%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%20I%20came%20in%20under%20budget%20by%20%2413%2C%20even%20with%20the%20mid-week%20grocery%20trips%20and%20the%20dog%20show%20empanada%20(and%20not%20counting%20the%20Sunday%20freebies%20or%20Saturday%20cheat%20meal).%20But%20being%20on%20%3Cem%3Esuch%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20strict%20diet%20and%20budget%20did%20lead%20to%20some%20notable%20limitations.%20My%20regimen%20lacked%20any%20appreciable%20amount%20of%20variety%2C%20and%20it%20made%20eating%20into%20an%20act%20focused%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20Dickison%2C%20the%20dietitian%2C%20for%20a%20final%20rating%20of%20my%20adventure%20once%20I%20wrap%20it%20up.%20She%20says%20that%2C%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20I%20have%20room%20for%20improvement%20with%20fruits%20and%20veggies%2C%20commends%20my%20integration%20of%20chickpeas%20and%20lentils%2C%20and%20says%20I%20did%20a%20good%20job%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommon-mistake-equation-calculating-protein-goal-needs-weight-loss-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein%20at%20every%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20I%20was%20too%20heavy%20on%20ground%20beef.%20The%20budget%20piece%20of%20this%20undertaking%20is%20the%20hardest%20part%2C%20she%20says.%20It%20makes%20it%20challenging%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20the%20new%20food%20pyramid%20recommendations%2C%20such%20as%20berries%2C%20fresh%20vegetables%2C%20and%20fish%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20aligned%20with%20how%20people%20live.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20speaking%20with%20patients%2C%20we%20talk%20about%20all%20the%20different%20ways%20that%20you%20get%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Sure%2C%20sometimes%20it's%20cooking%20at%20home%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslop-bowl-slowdown-chipotle-cava-sweetgreen-sales-struggling-rto-prices-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efast%20casual%20at%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20restaurant%20on%20a%20night%20out%2C%20or%20delivery%20when%20people%20are%20pressed%20for%20time.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20convenient%20the%20option%2C%20the%20more%20expensive%20it%20gets%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20also%20unrealistic%3A%20The%20ability%20to%20religiously%20follow%20such%20a%20rigid%20diet%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time.%20Hunger%20levels%20and%20cravings%20matter.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20really%20difficult%20to%20manage%20those%20biological%20drives%20and%20also%20this%20premeditated%20budget%2C%20even%20if%20you%20did%20have%20the%20best%20intentions%2C%26quot%3B%20Dickison%20says.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20text%20her%20every%20day%20for%20food%20advice%2C%20but%20I%20fear%20she%20would%20block%20my%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20funny%20little%20food%20journey%20of%20mine%20has%20coincided%20with%20a%20giant%20internet%20debate%20about%20some%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcut-doordash-deliveries-health-improved-saved-money-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20DoorDash%20too%20much%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20scolding%20them%20for%20not%20cooking%20more%20at%20home.%20After%20a%20week%20of%20being%20bound%20to%20team%20cook-at-home%2C%20I'm%20overly%20sympathetic%20to%20team%20DoorDash%2C%20if%20only%20because%20I've%20spent%20the%20past%20week%20envisioning%20the%20treat%20I'm%20about%20to%20get%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20via%20my%20delivery%20app%20of%20choice%2C%20Seamless%20%E2%80%94%20now%20that%20this%20is%20all%20over.%20Variety%20is%2C%20as%20the%20eye-rolling%20adage%20goes%2C%20the%20spice%20of%20life.%20Being%20able%20to%20switch%20up%20not%20only%20the%20dish%20but%20also%20the%20delivery%20method%20from%20time%20to%20time%20is%20part%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20has%20made%20clear%20the%20sacrifices%20we%20constantly%20make%20around%20affordability%2C%20sustenance%2C%20and%20gratification%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food.%20The%20cheapest%20option%20is%20never%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20The%20healthiest%20option%20is%20never%20the%20most%20thrilling%20option.%20The%20most%20thrilling%20option%20may%20be%20the%20cheapest%2C%20but%20it's%20usually%20bad%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20economic%20issue%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20cultural%20and%20political.%20When%20people%20on%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20income%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-will-be-banned-for-snap-users-2026-by-state-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eor%20public%20benefits%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20are%20told%20to%20focus%20on%20whole-food%20basics%2C%20they're%20told%20to%20give%20up%20on%20ease%20and%20joy%20as%20well.%20When%20people%20rely%20too%20much%20on%20delivery%2C%20they're%20almost%20certainly%20overspending%2C%20but%20they%20do%20so%20because%20it%20saves%20time%20and%20energy%20compared%20to%20an%20elaborate%20kitchen%20production.%20It's%20true%20that%20it's%20generally%20better%20to%20cook%20real%20meals%20with%20fresh%20ingredients%20at%20home.%20It's%20also%20true%20that%20life%20is%20complicated%2C%20and%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20that's%20not%20always%20possible.%20I%20probably%20could%20have%20stretched%20my%20budget%20just%20as%20far%2C%20if%20not%20farther%2C%20with%20frozen%2C%20preprepared%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20for%20most%20of%20us%2C%20dinner%20is%20less%20of%20an%20ideological%20project%20than%20it%20is%20a%20daily%20logistical%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20has%20to%20be%20solved%2C%20night%20after%20night%2C%20in%20perpetuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-food-pyramid-diet-guidelines-experience-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1770800821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698b9592e1ba468a96abcccc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-food-pyramid-diet-guidelines-experience-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20White%20House%20and%20HHS%20Secretary%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20have%20