soak%20up%20significant%20energy%20and%20require%20a%20power%20source%20in%20the%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENefor%20said%20his%20company%20deploys%20roughly%2020%20EcoFlow%20portable%20batteries%2C%20but%20there%20aren't%20enough%20to%20cover%20all%20its%20frontline%20positions.%20The%20batteries%20are%20also%20needed%20to%20power%20screens%20and%20radios%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20soldiers%20instead%20carry%20personal%20power%20banks%20to%20keep%20their%20devices%20charged.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20power%20bank%20you%20buy%20at%20the%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20Nefor%20said.%20%26quot%3BPower%20banks%20with%20Type-C%20or%20USB%20ports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f365c3c7-fceb-4899-8267-88d343eb2cd6%5C%22%3E'If%20you%20are%20not%20dry%2C%20you%20die'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECold%20temperatures%20can%20grow%20even%20more%20dangerous%20when%20they%20alternate%20between%20above%20and%20below%20freezing.%20Clothes%2C%20especially%20in%20humid%20areas%2C%20can%20absorb%20thawed%20water%20that%20can%20then%20freeze%20again%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20hypothermia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20not%20dry%2C%20you%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20Nefor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20this%20saying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClothing%20that%20gets%20wet%20in%20the%20winter%20stays%20wet%2C%20so%20troops%20who%20need%20dry%20layers%20have%20to%20request%20new%20ones%20from%20their%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unit-dedicated-fighting-russia-ground-assault-robots-ugvs-nc13-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUncrewed%20ground%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20recently%20been%20a%20major%20boon%20for%20Nefor's%20company%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20freeing%20up%20human%20soldiers%20by%20carrying%20weeks'%20worth%20of%20ammunition%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20other%20supplies%20such%20as%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20chemical%20warmers%20to%20the%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirearms%20and%20ammunition%20can%20become%20waterlogged%20as%20well.%20Nefor%20said%20that%20his%20troops%2C%20worried%20that%20their%20weapons%20would%20freeze%20up%2C%20apply%20a%20lubricating%20concoction%20to%20their%20rifles%20that%20mostly%20includes%20vehicle%20oil%20and%20sometimes%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20antifreeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20make%20one%2C%20two%20shots%20with%20your%20weapon%20to%20make%20it%20warmer%2C%20then%20you%20add%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Nefor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20commanders%20said%20the%20deep%20winter%20adds%20to%20the%20mental%20toll%20on%20Ukraine's%20already-beset%20troops%2C%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-mykhailo-fedorov-troop-shortage-awol-draft-dodging-2-million-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoften%20short%20on%20reinforcements%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20grinding%20nature%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENefor's%20company%20sends%20smaller%20groups%20of%20two%20or%20three%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20no%20more%20than%20four%20%E2%80%94%20to%20each%20position%20to%20avoid%20detection%20from%20Russian%20drones.%20Each%20soldier%20takes%20turns%20for%20several%20hours%20in%20the%20trenches%20between%20watch%20positions%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20colder%2C%20and%20warmer%20resting%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrieiev%20said%20that%20if%20he%20had%20more%20drone%20pilots%2C%20he%20could%20rotate%20them%20out%20of%20the%20front%20lines%20every%20four%20or%20five%20days.%20His%20teams%20instead%20spend%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20at%20a%20time%20in%20the%20forests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20exhausting%20to%20spend%20all%20that%20time%20in%20freezing%20temperatures.%20Even%20if%20you%20have%20heaters%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrieiev%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroops%20need%20more%20fuel%20and%20more%20clothes%20to%20perform%20their%20duties%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20task%20as%20simple%20as%20using%20an%20improvised%20bathroom%20in%20the%20trenches%20is%20stressful%2C%20with%20the%20soldier%20under%20threat%20from%20Russian%20drones%20while%20wearing%20multiple%20layers%2C%20body%20armor%2C%20and%20carrying%20their%20military%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-using-meat-assault-attacks-to-find-ukraine-firepower-bbc-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Russian%20assaults%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20have%20to%20fight%20off%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20stay%20just%20as%20frequent%20and%20intense%20during%20cold%20weeks%2C%20Andrieiev%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20the%20weather%20is.%20They%20come%20at%20us%20like%20zombies%2C%20two%20or%20three%20guys%20at%20a%20time%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20frozen%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-infantry-drone-pilot-survive-deep-winter-trenches-war-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1770786182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69899b4ca645d1188188f1a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-infantry-drone-pilot-survive-deep-winter-trenches-war-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20temperatures%20fell%20as%20low%20as%20-6%C2%B0F%20on%20some%20nights%2C%20Ukrainian%20troops%20had%20to%20lean%20on%20an%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-infantry-drone-pilot-survive-deep-winter-trenches-war-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mecca%20unveils%20Blue%20Quran%3A%20Viral%20pictures%20of%201%2C100-year-old%20masterpiece%20with%20Surah%20Al-Baqarah%20verses%20break%20the%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1770785279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiim